Leadership
Dexcom Leadership | John Lister








GM, Europe, Middle East & Africa
John Lister




John Lister is General Manager, Europe, Middle East & Africa. In this capacity, Mr. Lister oversees Dexcom's business and commercial affairs in the region, including strategic planning, operations and management of sales, distribution and marketing. Mr. Lister has been with Dexcom since 2008, and previously led both the legal and human resources groups. Prior to joining Dexcom, Mr. Lister served as an attorney with Fenwick & West where he specialized in corporate finance, mergers and acquisitions, startups, and general business matters for life sciences and technology companies. Mr. Lister received a BA from Claremont McKenna College, and a JD from the University of San Francisco. Mr. Lister is a member of the State Bar of California. 






















